{
  "$comment": "VENDORED copy — pinned for offline cross-repo conformance. Upstream: bicameral-sdk:src/evidence/index.ts + src/provenance/index.ts @ commit 180415bba0d7d777f8d1ce2ce3a5b81b29de1842 (GH #7); pinned 2026-06-18. The SDK ships TypeScript interfaces only (no JSON schema); this schema mirrors them. Re-verify on SDK evidence/provenance changes; integrations fails first on drift (FX-EVIDENCE-001).",
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "title": "Evidence",
